model_specification:
F = token_self/(token_self+token_opp)*combined_earning
U_accept = split_self - alpha*max(F - split_self,0) - beta*max(split_self - F,0)
model_summary: A fairness-based utility model for responder behavior that computes a fair share based on token contributions and penalizes deviations from this norm. Two learnable parameters modulate the sensitivity to disadvantageous and advantageous deviations, yielding a utility value that maps to the probability of acceptance.
